### Pagamentos - webhook (body)
POST {{base}}/pagamentos/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"type": "payment",
	"data": {
		"id": "3387807601-793c9ed3-2218-47a4-970f-464a914f33f2"
	}
}

### Pagamentos - webhook (query string)
POST {{base}}/pagamentos/webhook?data.id=1234567890
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Estornos - criar estorno por pagamento
POST {{base}}/pagamentos/1/estornos
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"motivo": "cancelamento",
	"valor": "120.00"
}